THIRD-PARTY ACKNOWLEDGMENTS:

This software builds upon and includes components from the following projects:

1. SocialMapper (https://github.com/uklibaite/SocialMapper)
   - License: As specified in the original repository
   - Components: MotionMapper utilities, behavioral embedding algorithms
   - Copyright: Original authors of SocialMapper

2. MotionMapper Framework
   - Based on: Berman et al. (2014) Journal of The Royal Society Interface
   - Components: Core behavioral embedding methodology

3. ComBat Batch Correction
   - Based on: Johnson et al. (2007) Biostatistics  
   - Components: Batch correction algorithms

This pipeline maintains compatibility with the original licenses while adding
specialized functionality for neuroscience applications.

Users must comply with the licenses of all included components.

For detailed attribution information, see ACKNOWLEDGMENTS.md